        </div>
        <p>Undeniably, unsealed sheathing to frame gaps (which, as mentioned above, can account for 50% of air leakage), when taken together, greatly contribute to the stack effect and energy loss in all climate conditions and offer a likely target for mitigation of the problem. The <i>AccuFrame<sup><small>&reg;</small></sup> Energy Seal</i> method is designed to fill this 'gap' and is an economical effective solution to eliminating unwanted air infiltration.</p>
